wiki.summary: “No Way!” is the third track from Bazzi’s first mixtape "Soul Searching". Written by the American artist himself, in this track Bazzi talks about how much his life have changed since being in the music industry. He states that from now on he keeps moving forward and that there’s nothing holding him back. Read more on Last.fm.
